<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-container">
    <h1 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>How do I contact customer support?</h3>
      <p>Our official customer support channel is through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> on our website.</p>
      <p>All concerns regarding product availability, orders, deliveries, and returns are handled exclusively through this channel to ensure proper assistance.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- STORE HOURS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Is the online store open 24/7?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Our online store is open 24/7, except during brief system maintenance periods, which usually occur late at night.</p>
      <p>Our fulfillment and support teams operate from Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- TRACKING -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>When will I receive my tracking number?</h3>
      <p>Tracking numbers are generated within a few hours to a few days after payment confirmation, depending on order volume and location. You’ll receive an email notification once your tracking number becomes available.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>How can I track my order?</h3>
      <p>You can track your order by logging into your <a href="/users/login">Commonwealth account</a> and viewing your order history. You will also receive tracking details via email once your order has been shipped.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ORDER PROGRESS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Where can I view my order details?</h3>
      <p>Log in to your <a href="/users/login">Commonwealth account</a> to access your full order history. Simply click on the order number you wish to review for updates and shipment status.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- PROCESSING -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>When will my order be processed?</h3>
      <p>Orders are processed once payment has been successfully confirmed. For same-day processing, please complete your order before 12:00 PM. Orders placed after this time will be processed the next business day.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Do you accept orders during weekends or holidays?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Orders can be placed at any time, including weekends and holidays. However, processing will resume on the next business day.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- PAYMENT -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
      <p>We accept major debit and credit cards, GCash, Maya, and bank transfers. Available payment options will be shown during checkout.</p>
      <p>Some limited-edition releases may require manual payment confirmation. In such cases:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>You’ll receive an email with payment instructions.</li>
        <li>Attach your proof of payment along with your order number and send it via the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</li>
        <li>Wait for an official confirmation email once your payment has been verified.</li>
      </ol>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Orders will automatically be cancelled if payment is not received within the specified time frame.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CONFIRMATION -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Will I receive a confirmation after placing my order?</h3>
      <p>Yes. You’ll receive an order confirmation email immediately after checkout, followed by another email once your order has been shipped with tracking details included.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- PICKUP -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Can I pick up my order from a Commonwealth store?</h3>
      <p>At the moment, in-store pickup is unavailable. Online and in-store operations are handled separately to ensure smooth processing and inventory management.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- DELIVERY -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>I have not received my order yet. What should I do?</h3>
      <p>Delivery timelines are estimates and may vary due to external factors such as weather conditions, customs processing, or courier delays. You will receive updates via email, and you can also check your <a href="/users/login">Commonwealth account</a> for order status.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SHIPPING INFO -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>I entered the wrong shipping details. Can I still change them?</h3>
      <p>If your order hasn’t been dispatched yet, we can update your shipping details. Please send the correct information through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> as soon as possible.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CANCELLATIONS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Can I cancel or modify my order?</h3>
      <p>Once an order has been placed and confirmed, modifications and cancellations are no longer allowed. For urgent concerns, you may reach out through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- REFUNDS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Refunds for cancelled or unavailable orders</h3>
      <p>If your order was cancelled due to stock unavailability or a system error, a refund will automatically be processed to your original payment method.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Debit / Credit Cards:</strong> 7–45 banking days</li>
        <li><strong>GCash / Maya / QR PH:</strong> 7–15 banking days</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Actual reflection time depends on your bank or e-wallet provider.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- DAMAGED ITEMS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>I received a damaged item. What should I do?</h3>
      <p>Please send clear photos or videos of the damaged product through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>. If a replacement is available, we’ll send it immediately. Otherwise, we’ll issue a refund through your original payment method.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>The product box was damaged. Can I request a replacement?</h3>
      <p>We handle packaging concerns on a case-by-case basis. Minor box creases are not eligible for replacement, but significant damage will be reviewed and addressed accordingly.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- AVAILABILITY -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Can you check if a certain size or product is available?</h3>
      <p>All available products are updated in real-time on our website. Some items may be exclusive to online or physical stores.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SIZING -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>How can I find my size?</h3>
      <p>Please visit our <a href="/sizing">Size Guide</a> for complete sizing information. For additional assistance, contact us via the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- RAFFLE -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>How do I join Commonwealth raffles?</h3>
      <p>Announcements for raffle releases are made on our social media pages. Entries can be submitted through our <a href="/raffle">Raffle page</a> once the raffle opens.</p>
      <p>All raffle purchases are considered final and non-transferable. Commonwealth reserves the right to disqualify entries that violate our policies.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- HOTLINE -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>Do you have a customer service hotline?</h3>
      <p>We currently do not have a phone hotline. For inquiries, please reach us through the <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> or message us on our official social media channels.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- SHIPPING -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>What is your shipping policy?</h3>
      <p>For complete information on shipping timelines and delivery coverage, please visit our <a href="/shipping">Shipping Information page</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- RETURNS -->
    <div class="faq-block">
      <h3>What is your return policy?</h3>
      <p>To learn more about returns and exchanges, please visit our <a href="/returns">Returns & Exchanges page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
